# Secrets must never enter the build context / image. Exclude every env file
# except the committed placeholder. .env holds real dev secrets (DB, migration
# superuser, auth/OAuth, master key) and Next.js standalone tracing otherwise
# copies it into .next/standalone → the final image.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
.claude
*.md
.vscode
.idea
